726381f-a.text:
Cooper Ave., east of 66th Place (formerly Gamma Fiace) to 67th Place (formerly Alpha Mace Place) showing in the foreground the Denton House, formerly numbered 2709 and which is now. No 6653. The three storied structure in the center of view, is at the N.E. corner of Cooper Ave. and 67th Street (formerly Beta Street).

April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
